That bullshit! I've just downloaded the episode - fully functional...

VLC and some other mediaplayers can play partially downloaded files so its easy to check for fakes without getting the whole thing (although you often need the first chunk).

Some bittorrent clients can also prioritize start pieces of torrents.

In any case ignore afkuser, I suspect antipiracy groups are posting fake comments (although in this case he is probably just an idiot).
